                    <li class="regularitem">
                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/JQ-wOnSBS0g/">Switch OLED 新版香港預訂日期  &nbsp; OLED 熒幕 + 硬件規格</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Wed, 08 Sep 2021 08:31:31 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p>任天堂香港今日公佈，全新版本 Nintendo Switch 將會與日本同步，於 9 月 24 日開始正式開始接受訂購，新主機會在 10 月 8 日正式發售。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>今次新推出的「Nintendo Switch OLED 款式」擁有全新 7 吋的 OLED 熒幕，除了畫質加強外，尺寸比起現時版本的 6.2 吋熒幕更大。解像度方面就維持 1280 x 720，電視輸出為 1920 x 1080 像素高清輸出。「OLED 款式」還將內置儲存空間由原來的 32GB 提升至 64GB。至於主機晶片、圖像處理器等配置就同現時款式相同。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.50-694x300.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="300" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.50-694x300.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.50-768x333.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.50.jpg 1074w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>新款主機另有更大型的豎起背面的支架，在桌面上豎起遊玩時會更穩陣。此支架還採用轉軸式設計，可讓用戶自由調節角度（現行版本不能自由調節角度）。另主機也內置有全新喇叭。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_tablemode.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_tablemode-443x580.png" alt="" width="443" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_tablemode-443x580.png 443w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_tablemode.png 536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 443px" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>此外新機的附屬底座將會預設有 LAN 有線網絡的插孔，上網打機就不怕延遲問題。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.24.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1058778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.31.24.jpg" alt="" width="655" height="421" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_detail_lan.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pic_detail_lan.jpg" alt="" width="510" height="181" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>想訂購的玩家，可從 9 月 24 日開始，於官方指定的銷售店鋪訂購，詳細地址可參考<a href="https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/?fbclid=IwAR2otmUGmecdEyiN83Gem7OSxz2OnG_fhH-UkoF32DWAQBk1djqwgEgiJy0">官方網站</a>。價格與之前的版本一樣，同為 HK$2,680。主機備有白色 Joy-Con、底座版本，以及經典的紅藍 Joy-Con 版本。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17-694x563.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="563" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17-694x563.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17-1109x900.jpg 1109w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17-768x623.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-15.19.17.jpg 1315w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/detail/switch-oled/">Nintendo</a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/08/nintendo-switch-3/game-channel/">Switch OLED 新版香港預訂日期    OLED 熒幕 + 硬件規格</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=JQ-wOnSBS0g:gulST0ZNqQ4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=JQ-wOnSBS0g:gulST0ZNqQ4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/JQ-wOnSBS0g" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></div>
