                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/BVGwyZsOLh4/">The Matrix 4 互動前導影片&nbsp;   選擇紅藍藥丸 + 18 萬種不同影片</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Wed, 08 Sep 2021 07:29:19 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p>科幻動作影片《The Matrix: Resurrections》（22世紀殺人網絡 復活次元）將會預定於 2021 年上映，而最近官方就發表了預告影片，影片原來有互動成份，畫面會要求觀眾選擇紅色藥丸，或者藍色藥丸，你會看到有不同電影預告片段！</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>想睇到 The Matrix: Resurrections 前導影片中，紅藍藥丸背後隱藏的片段，單看 YouTube 片是看不到的。你要到 <a href="https://thechoiceisyours.whatisthematrix.com/en/">官方網站</a> ，在網頁的頁面就可點選紅色或藍色藥丸，背後有兩段內容不同的前導影片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058752" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-1280x776.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-1536x931.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1-2048x1242.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.20.06-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>點擊後畫面會浮現出你進入頁面的時間，根據時間畫面會顯示出不同排列組合的前導影片。根據外媒消息，總共會有 18 萬種排列方式，你看到的影片在排列上極有可能同你朋友看的不同！網頁不限制前導影片觀看次數，所以你可不斷嘗試看看。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-1280x713.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-768x428.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-1536x855.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-2048x1140.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.30-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058756" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-1280x788.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-768x473.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-1536x946.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-2048x1261.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-08-下午1.24.57-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《The Matrix: Resurrections》（22世紀殺人網絡 復活次元）較完整的預告影片，將會在明日（9日）公開，有興趣的朋友就要留意官方網站了。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>《The Matrix: Resurrections》電影由去年 2 月開拍，受到疫情影響有一段時間停拍，及後於去年 8 月重開。此電影是《Matrix》的第 4 部作品，為 2003 年《22 世紀殺人網絡3：驚變世紀》的續集。影片由華高斯基執導，並有奇洛李維斯、嘉利安慕絲、珍達史密夫、林拔韋遜與丹尼爾伯恩哈特主演。影片預定在 2021 年 12 月 22 日在美國上映。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72228"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332"  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wdskyfJtyt8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://thechoiceisyours.whatisthematrix.com/en/">官方網站</a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/08/the-matrix-resurrections/hottopic/">The Matrix 4 互動前導影片    選擇紅藍藥丸 + 18 萬種不同影片</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=BVGwyZsOLh4:PqufYgzHCNs:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=BVGwyZsOLh4:PqufYgzHCNs:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/BVGwyZsOLh4" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></div>
