                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/y89TGGuwCkc/">Apple iPhone 13 發佈日期 + 直播連結  &nbsp; 官網AR彩蛋 + 觀看方法</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Wed, 08 Sep 2021 05:06:22 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p>Apple 宣佈將會在香港時間 2021 年 9 月 15 日上午 1 時，舉行特別新作發表會。預計將會發表 2021 年一系列全新 iPhone 智能手機，更有機會發表全新 Apple Watch Series 7、全新 AirPods 等產品。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Apple 指用戶可透過 Apple <a href="https://www.apple.com">官方網站</a>，或者 Apple TV 收看在香港時間 2021 年 9 月 15 日深夜 1 時舉行的發表會。根據以往慣例，他們亦有在 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EvGOlAkLSLw">YouTube</a> 平台直播。直播中相信 Apple 會發表包括 iPhone 13, Apple Watch 7 甚至全新 AirPods 等新產品。傳聞指 iPhone 13 將會縮細畫面頂部「M 字額」瀏海的面積、搭載 120Hz 高流暢度顯示器，相機鏡頭硬件以及軟件配套都會有所提升。有興趣了解的朋友可閱讀早前的<a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/06/iphone13newssummary/mobile-phone/">文章</a>。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_68922"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332"  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EvGOlAkLSLw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>發表會宣傳海報有彩蛋</h2><p>今次發表會的宣傳資料原來都有彩蛋。只要你在手機的瀏覽器進入今次發表會的宣傳網站：<a href="https://www.apple.com/apple-events/">http://www.apple.com/apple-events</a>，然後點擊畫面中的 Apple 標誌，稍等一下，就會出現一個 AR 小遊戲。在你的現實世界中，會出現一個 Apple 標誌，你可行近這個標誌，然後窺看到裡面的發表會日期以及星星。有指這裡出現的星星代表了 iPhone 13 將會推出的星空拍攝功能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-768x1663.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-709x1536.png 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002-946x2048.png 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0002.png 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲首先點擊官方<a href="https://www.apple.com/apple-events/">宣傳網站</a>的 Apple 標誌</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001.png"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058702 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-768x1663.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-709x1536.png 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-946x2048.png 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001.png 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲稍等一下，畫面就會出現圖中的 AR 遊戲，在現實世界中會出現 Apple 標誌</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000.png"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1058704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-768x1663.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-709x1536.png 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-946x2048.png 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003.png 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲這個標誌會慢慢放大，然後你會看到發表會日期（香港時間），細心留意還會看到上方的星空</p><p>相關影片：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Definitely the best <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AppleEvent?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AppleEvent</a> AR Easter egg so far <a href="https://t.co/RxEMEGCTEN">pic.twitter.com/RxEMEGCTEN</a></p><p>&mdash; Guilherme Rambo (@_inside) <a href="https://twitter.com/_inside/status/1435279519942778881?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 7, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>受疫情影響，去年 Apple 分別在 9 月以及 10 月舉行新產品發表會，將 iPhone 與 Apple Watch 分開發表，今次或有可能一次過發表這些新產品。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/apple-events/">Apple</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/_inside/status/1435279519942778881">Twitter</a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/08/appleevents2021/mobile-phone/">Apple iPhone 13 發佈日期 + 直播連結    官網AR彩蛋 + 觀看方法</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=y89TGGuwCkc:LqAFBvpBtQs:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=y89TGGuwCkc:LqAFBvpBtQs:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
